Package dungeon

Class Room

java.lang.Object
dungeon.Room
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Tile>
public class Room
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Tile>, java.lang.Cloneable
A Room is a rectangle of tiles with meta-info (description and level in the dungeon). Is built with a room builder
